reviewText: Good quality, although very cheesy narration and video use. The women are absolutely stunning, hearstoppingly beautiful, but there is NO nudity. I wasn't looking for pornography, just something along the lines of the  magazine, which I really enjoy by the way. But this disappointed me, I got  it because I am missing issues of the magazine and wanted to see the women  from them. It didn't happen. Overall, I would recommend against this video  if you are looking for a little nudity or erotica.
